{"text": " The purpose of this practice is to stabilize the mind and its attention on a single and very subtle object the air. Let us start by observing the airflow in and out of the body. Observe the air coming out of your body, going in. Coming out, observe the breathing and the airflow. Watch how the air is coming out of your body on an exhalation and see how that air meets the air outside of you. The air coming into you from outside. The air coming out and merging with the air outside of you right in front of your face. Now witness the presence of air in front of you. Let the body breathe by itself. Just observe how the breathing process is happening by itself without your help. Simply be a witness. Witness the breathing without participating. See how the body breathes by itself. Now witness the presence of air in front of you. Do not follow the airflow, simply witness the presence of air. Do not follow the air movement. Witness the presence of air in front of you. See how the body breathes by itself. Do not follow and simply witness how the body breathes by itself. How the air is moving on its own. How it's all happening on its own without your participation. Do not follow the air movement. And be a pure witness of air in front of you. Do not follow the air. Do not follow your breathing. Wait and witness the presence of air. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow your breathing. Continue to witness the presence of air. Do not follow your breathing. Do not follow the air. Do not follow the air movement. How everything is happening by itself. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the breathing. Stay a pure witness. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Stay a pure witness. The body is bringing on its own. The air in front of you. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement. Do not follow the air movement.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 12.540000000000001, "end": 25.84, "text": " The purpose of this practice is to stabilize the mind and its attention on a single and", "tokens": [50364, 440, 4334, 295, 341, 3124, 307, 281, 31870, 264, 1575, 293, 1080, 3202, 322, 257, 2167, 293, 51656], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1659599712916783, "compression_ratio": 1.16, "no_speech_prob": 0.016844453290104866, "words": [{"word": " The", "start": 12.540000000000001, "end": 13.62, "probability": 0.9445004463195801}, {"word": " purpose", "start": 13.62, "end": 13.92, "probability": 0.9941397905349731}, {"word": " of", "start": 13.92, "end": 14.26, "probability": 0.9957386255264282}, {"word": " this", "start": 14.26, "end": 14.42, "probability": 0.9970581531524658}, {"word": " practice", "start": 14.42, "end": 14.88, "probability": 0.9801080822944641}, {"word": " is", "start": 14.88, "end": 16.4, "probability": 0.9639514088630676}, {"word": " to", "start": 16.4, "end": 16.58, "probability": 0.998034656047821}, {"word": " stabilize", "start": 16.58, "end": 17.24, "probability": 0.9771879315376282}, {"word": " the", "start": 17.24, "end": 18.9, "probability": 0.956707775592804}, {"word": " mind", "start": 18.9, "end": 19.32, "probability": 0.9923428893089294}, {"word": " and", "start": 19.32, "end": 20.52, "probability": 0.9639081358909607}, {"word": " its", "start": 20.52, "end": 20.76, "probability": 0.9484928250312805}, {"word": " attention", "start": 20.76, "end": 21.34, "probability": 0.9935762286186218}, {"word": " on", "start": 21.34, "end": 22.92, "probability": 0.9411942362785339}, {"word": " a", "start": 22.92, "end": 23.04, "probability": 0.9969685673713684}, {"word": " singl